11. Limitations
The system depends on the availability and accuracy of external financial data sources such as the yfinance API.
Financial models rely on historical data, which may not always accurately predict future market behavior.
Continuous internet connectivity is required for real-time data processing and API integration.
The system is designed as a decision-support tool and should not be considered a substitute for professional financial advisory services.
